  "html": "<h2 class=\"\" id=\"morningradio\">MorningRadio</h2>\n<p class=\"\">Designed to be a healthy \"first screen\" in the morning. News summaries, updates, and enough information about the latest events that you don't feel the need to endlessly doomscroll.</p>\n<p class=\"\">The goal was to repurpose the tik-tok style endless vertical scroll but instead fill it with interesting and useful websites, tools, and news articles (populated through my Pinboard bookmarks)</p>\n<p class=\"\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,dpr_auto,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_800/v1755098720/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.25.04_AM.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,dpr_auto,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_400/v1755098720/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.25.04_AM.png 400w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,dpr_auto,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_800/v1755098720/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.25.04_AM.png 800w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,dpr_auto,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1200/v1755098720/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.25.04_AM.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" style=\"background-color:#222222;background-image:url(&#x22;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20width%3D%22978%22%20height%3D%222086%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%20978%202086%22%20preserveAspectRatio%3D%22none%22%3E%3Cdefs%3E%3ClinearGradient%20id%3D%22g%22%20x1%3D%220%22%20y1%3D%220%22%20x2%3D%221%22%20y2%3D%221%22%3E%3Cstop%20offset%3D%220%25%22%20stop-color%3D%22%23222222%22%2F%3E%3Cstop%20offset%3D%22100%25%22%20stop-color%3D%22%23333333%22%2F%3E%3C%2FlinearGradient%3E%3C%2Fdefs%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%22100%25%22%20height%3D%22100%25%22%20fill%3D%22url(%23g)%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E&#x22;);background-size:cover;background-position:center;\" data-placeholder=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%2